features: [Brand Overview] THERMALRIGHT is a Taiwanese brand with more than 20 years of development history. It has a certain degree of popularity in the Chinese market and has a decisive influence in the cooler market. We have been focusing on the research and development of computer peripheral accessories. The R&D product line includes: CPU coolers, CPU liquid coolers, case fans, thermal paste, accessories and other products.

【AGHP technique】4x6mm heatpipe with AGHP upgraded 4th generation technology, the Inverse gravity effect caused by vertical / horizontal orientation. Up to 20000 hours of industrial service life, S-FDB bearings ensure long service life of air-cooler radiators. UL class a safety insulation low-grade, industrial strength PBT + PC material to create high-quality products for you. The height is 118mm, compatible with a wide range of chassis models.

【Product specification】 AX90SE ARGB; CPU Cooler dimensions:94(L)x77(W)x118(H)mm (3.7x3.0x 4.65 inch); Heat sink material: aluminum, the main body adopts HDT direct touch process and fine pure copper surface treatment, the main body is fully aluminum fins to bring the maximum cooling area, combined with high speed fans, can perfectly play the cooler's most powerful cooling effect.

【PWM Fan】 TL-P9-S; Standard size industrial grade PWM performance PC fan: 92x92x25mm (3.6x3.6x0.98 inches); Fan speed (RPM): 2200rpm±10%; Power port: 4-pin; Voltage: 12V; Air flow: 32.77CFM (max); Noise level ≤23.85dB(A), high performance fan combined with efficient heat dissipation The heatsink cooling body of the unit gives you the best cooling effect.

[RAM AVOIDANCE DESIGN] The computer cpu cooling is designed with a skewed memory avoidance design, which will not be restricted from mounting due to the height of the memory, and the main body is made of nano fully sprayed black paint, which makes the radiator offset easy to mount.

【Compatibility】The CPU cooling slot support: Intel: 1150/1151/1155/1156/1200/1700/17XX, AMD: AM4/AM5; for different CPU slot platforms, provide the corresponding mounting plate or fasteners, can be combined with the installation instructions or follow the tutorial to get on the machine.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars A great product for a reasonable price
reviews.reviewText: My HP OMEN 25L computer is very bad in terms of airflow so the Ryzen 7 3700x cpu runs hot, the cpu throttles. The Cooler Master 212 EVO wouldn't fit the case as the case width is small. After doing some research I purchased this heat sink. After opening the case I found that HP is not using the standard AM4 holes in its motherboard, so I couldn't use this heatsink. But the build quality seems on par with 212 EVO.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worked fine for my smaller case
reviews.reviewText: Have a really old rose will case no room for big boi cooler. Running it in my "server" with a 3700x hosting ark ascended valheim and my unifi networking containers. 55 degrees stable no issues. Easy install (do have to hold plate on back while screwing in but motherboard was out anyway) but could be challenging if mobo is in case (just hold it from back). Quiet easy peasy.
